flowchart TD
  Upload[Stream .forge upload] --> Store[Atomic artifact store + SHA-256]
  Store --> Validate[Archive and manifest validation]
  Validate -->|invalid| Rejected[Package REJECTED\nfindings retained]
  Validate -->|valid| Accepted[Package VALIDATED\ncontract retained]
  Accepted --> Create[Create idempotent deployment operation]
  Create --> Intent[Persist BUILDING desired state]
  Intent --> Generate[Generate deterministic runtime artifact]
  Generate --> Build[Build immutable Docker image]
  Build -->|failure| Failed[Attempt FAILED\nbounded logs + classified reason]
  Build -->|success| Start[Start constrained internal container]
  Start --> ReadyCheck[Readiness/health check]
  ReadyCheck -->|failure| Failed
  ReadyCheck -->|success| Ready[Version READY]
  Ready --> Activate[Acquire deployment lock\natomically update route]
  Activate -->|success| Active[Version ACTIVE\nstable prediction route]
  Activate -->|failure| Ready
  Active --> Replace[Activate replacement]
  Replace --> Ready
  Active --> Stop[Remove route then stop]
  Ready --> Stop
  Stop --> Stopped[Version STOPPED]
  Failed --> Retry[Explicit retry]
  Retry --> Create

